```dockerfile
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21 AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:go-offline

COPY src/ src/

RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

RUN apk add --no-cache \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    curl \
    ca-certificates

WORKDIR /app

RUN mkdir -p /tmp/certs

RUN curl -o /tmp/certs/rds-ca-2019-root.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2019-root.pem && \
    curl -o /tmp/certs/rds-ca-2015-root.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2015-root.pem && \
    curl -o /tmp/certs/digicert-global-root.pem https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt

RUN keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2019 -file /tmp/certs/rds-ca-2019-root.pem -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2015 -file /tmp/certs/rds-ca-2015-root.pem -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -import -alias digicert-global -file /tmp/certs/digicert-global-root.pem -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt

RUN rm -rf /tmp/certs

RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app

COPY --from=builder /build/target/app.jar /app/app.jar
RUN chown -R app:app /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=40s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
